Depends: libsilkit5, ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: bridge any socket and transmit veIPC (Vector Module for 
  Interprocessor Communication) messages between it and a pair of SIL 
  Kit Topics. The SIL Kit Adapter veIPC source and documentation is 
